Package: PatentSafeR
Title: Easily Submit to PatentSafe from R
Version: 0.0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Coles", , "simon.coles@amphora-research.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5680-5476"))
Description: The goal of PatentSafeR is to make it quick and easy to submit your experimental 
             work to the PatentSafe ELN from Amphora Research Systems. Support for this 
             package is provided with your PatentSafe support contract, so if you'd like
             assistance use the "Support" link on every PatentSafe page. 
